[normal]   
[normal]10)
[normal]&#xa0; 
[normal]Service Charges for Adaptations: [bold]Under Universal Credit the costs associated with special equipment and adaptations will be deemed as ineligible service charges. We understand that the support for these costs will be withdrawn completely with no transitional protection. 
[normal]These costs will t
[normal]herefore have to be fully met by the tenant
[normal],
[normal] many of whom will struggle to cover this additional expenditure
[normal].
[normal] 
[normal]T
[normal]his is another threat to the ability of disabled people to live independently.  
[normal]  
