[normal]o
[normal]f Horizon HA’s tenants
[normal] in general needs housing
[normal] and 31% of tenants who live in purpose built or adapted hous
[normal]ing have been awarded a DHP. Awards range from 3 months to 1 year and some local authorities take DLA into account in considering income available and others do not. 
